爱莎贝儿-140CM-M 粉肤 RAD056 雪村铃鹿Yukimura Suzuka-乱掉的心跳声

他睫毛扫过我掌心时，我飞快亲了他脸颊。
黑暗里只剩我们乱掉的心跳声。

Elsa Babe-140CM-M Pink RAD056 Yukimura Suzuka~ The Sound of Chaotic Heart Beating

As his eyelashes brushed against my palm, I quickly kissed his cheek.
Only the sound of our racing hearts remained in the darkness.
Body type: 140CM-M with Pink skin tone
